==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Preconcert
<hw>Pre*con"cert</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Something
concerted or arranged beforehand; a previous agreement.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

